WF-005 | Open Group detail from results | actor: <role> | branch: Selected result from Groups group | terminal: Open Detail | on_success: navigate_to_detail_page
WF-006 | Open Loan detail from results | actor: <role> | branch: Selected result from Loans group | terminal: Open Detail | on_success: navigate_to_detail_page
WF-007 | Open Savings detail from results | actor: <role> | branch: Selected result from Savings group | terminal: Open Detail | on_success: navigate_to_detail_page
